<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="less is more" class="zu-question-my-bio">less is more</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="796">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$sun-zhi-54-16" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/sun-zhi-54-16" class="zg-link" title="孫治">孫治</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yang-twii" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yang-twii" class="zg-link" title="yang Twii">yang Twii</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xie-dou-dou-1" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xie-dou-dou-1" class="zg-link" title="叶豆豆">叶豆豆</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2787343" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">谢邀。<br><br>不要一唱一和的秀。<br><br>不要两个人一起秀。<br><br>不要把说给对方听的话，秀到网上。<br><br>不要秀太肉麻的昵称。<br><br>不要为了证明感情而秀。<br><br>不要为了增加底气而秀。<br><br>不要为了惹人羡慕而秀。<br><br>不要为了秀而秀。<br><br>记下的只是生活，而生活中有她/他罢了。


</div>

</div>
</div>
